- [x] Request defaults: `limit=5`; optional `days` passthrough.
- [x] Parse `trendingMovies` payload into HomeVC model.
- [x] Map image fallback fields (`thumbnail_picture` then `large_picture`).

Phase 2 - HomeVC state foundation (`@ios-dev`)

- [x] Add `TrendingDisplayMode` enum (`carousel`, `list`).
- [x] Add HomeVC state fields: `trendingMovies`, `displayMode`, `isLoading`, `errorState`.
- [x] Ensure one data source is shared by carousel and list rendering.

Phase 3 - Carousel UI (`@ios-dev`)

- [x] Implement/default a horizontal carousel section in `HomeVC`.
- [x] Render maximum five movies.
- [x] Card content: poster + movie title.
- [x] Preserve backend response order.

Phase 4 - Swipe-down transform (`@ios-dev`)

- [x] Add downward swipe recognizer to trending section container.
- [x] Implement animated transition from carousel to list.
